    <string name="help_title">App Functionality</string>
    <string name="help_content">
        &lt;b&gt;Eyes-Free Awareness&lt;/b&gt;: Stay informed through unique sound patterns that distinguish between local threats and distant alerts, designed for use while driving or when the phone is in your pocket.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Situational Distinction&lt;/b&gt;: Each alert is audible country-wide, but the audio signature tells you the urgency and proximity without needing to look at the screen.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Less Intrusive&lt;/b&gt;: Provides a subtle but clear pulse of information, reducing the false-urgency fatigue of generic sirens.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Disclaimer&lt;/b&gt;: This is an unofficial tool. Always prioritize official instructions and sirens from the Home Front Command.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;Internal Alpha&lt;/b&gt;: You are using a development version for testing purposes. Please report any issues.
    </string>
